Final [Heysel Stadium, Brussels]

28-05-58 Real Madrid                3-2 Milan AC                 [aet]
          [Alfredo di Stéfano 74, José Héctor Rial 79, Francisco Gento 107;
           Juan Schiaffino 59, Ernesto Grillo 78]
Real Madrid: Juan Alonso (c); Ángel Atienza, José Santamaría, Rafael
   Lesmes, Juan Santistebán, José María Zárraga, Raymond Kopa,
